OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA mixed day with some bright
OL,6,Fand sunny spells but also blustery
OL,7,Fshowers feeding in from the west. Best
OL,8,Fof the sunny spells in the east.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,11,Fand strong winds spreading north on
OL,12,FSaturday with a risk of gales.
OL,13,FBlustery showers with gale risk easing
OL,14,Fon Sunday. Mostly dry with sunny
OL,15,Fspells Monday, windy west coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
